                  <p>NUMBER VII. PART IX.</p>
                  <p>LONDON:</p>
                  <p>Printed for E. HODGSON (the Proprietor); And Sold by him, at his House, No. 14, White Lion Street, Islington; Sold also by J. WALMSLAY, No. 35, Chancery Lane; S. BLADON, No. 31, Pater-noster Row; and J. MARSOM, No. 183, High Holborn.</p>
